prepared meals from consumers (with options for on-demand deliveries, scheduled deliveries and pick-up orders) through our
merchant-partner application and it also enables driver-partners to accept bookings for prepared meal delivery services
through our driver-partner application;
“GrabForGood Fund” means our endowment fund that aims to introduce and support programs that empower Southeast

Asian communities to improve socioeconomic mobility and quality of life;
“GrabHitch” refers to our carpooling booking service, which enables drivers other than our driver-partners, who sign up
through our platform, to accept bookings for carpool rides through our platform;
